content.html: Last year Google launched the Tech Career Training program supporting the Black community; today 56 of them graduated. I've spoken to this group three times along the way and today they brought me to tears. So far, 14 of them already landed tech jobs, but all of them inspire me.
content.value:
Last year Google launched the Tech Career Training program supporting the Black community; today 56 of them graduated. I've spoken to this group three times along the way and today they brought me to tears.

So far, 14 of them already landed tech jobs, but all of them inspire me.
